headline: Citi Names Texas Instruments Stock a Top Pick. Why It’s Set for a Recovery.
summary: After a challenging time for analog chips, a Citi analyst named  Texas Instruments  as a top stock pick.  Analog chips from companies such as Texas Instruments are used in the industrials, auto, and consumer electronics spaces.  Demand in the auto and industrial markets has been under pressure for some time following a surge of pandemic-related demand.
